{
  "stem": "1857.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They waited for us at the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My cousin was driving a 12-cylinder Lincoln.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, they made, in 1946, a 12-cylinder Lincoln with push-button doors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was the most expensive American car.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was standing at the railroad station with a very long cigar.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they brought us to their house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had lunch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And first, my cousin was showing me a banana.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He says, 'This is called banana.' And-- and he was showing us all kinds of things, and I thought that this was so ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said to my father, 'You know something?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't take it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who does he think we are?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where does he think we came from?' He says, 'Be nice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Be nice.' Then my cousin takes us into the alley.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, 'You see this car?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is the best American car.' He says, 'This is called automobile.'",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that moment, his wife calls him to the telephone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I get into the car, I start it, and I drive around the block.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Chicago, they parked the cars in the alley in the back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I came back into the alley, the whole family was standing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My cousin was pale.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, 'How did you know how to drive?' I said, 'Benny, I have an international driver's license.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't worry about it.' So he got on the telephone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He called all his friends. 'My greenhorn knows how to drive.' So I said to them, 'Look, I want to finish engineering.' So my cousin tells  me, says to me, 'In this country, you don't need education to make a success.' He says, 'Look at me.' He says, 'If you work for us long enough, you'll make, one day, $100 a week.'",
      "word_count": 62
    }
  ],
